OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772223642
OL,3,CUK withdraws staff from Iran amid
OL,4,Cthreat of US strikes
OL,6,FThe Foreign Office has "temporarily"
OL,7,Fwithdrawn its staff from Iran amid the
OL,8,Fthreat of US strikes against the
OL,9,Fcountry.
OL,11,FAn update to official travel advice on
OL,12,FFriday said: "Due to the ongoing
OL,13,Fsecurity situation, we have taken the
OL,14,Fprecautionary measure to temporarily
OL,15,Fwithdraw UK staff from Iran."
OL,17,FIt added that the British embassy
OL,18,F"continues to operate remotely" after
OL,19,Fit was closed in mid-January.
