OL,3,CUK withdraws staff from Iran amid
OL,4,Cthreat of US strikes
OL,6,FThe decision to withdraw UK staff
OL,7,Fcomes a day after talks between the US
OL,8,Fand Iran over its nuclear programme
OL,9,Fended without agreement.
OL,11,FPresident Donald Trump has previously
OL,12,Fthreatened to take military action
OL,13,Fagainst Iran if it does not reach a
OL,14,Fdeal on its nuclear programme, and the
OL,15,FUS has spent the last month amassing a
OL,16,Ffleet of aircraft and warships in the
OL,17,Fregion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
