OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772223642
OL,3,CUK withdraws staff from Iran amid
OL,4,Cthreat of US strikes
OL,6,FIran has, in turn, threatened to
OL,7,Fattack Israel, raising the risk that
OL,8,Fmilitary action could trigger another
OL,9,Fregional war.
OL,11,FOn Friday, US ambassador to Israel
OL,12,FMike Huckabee told his staff they
OL,13,Fcould leave the country if they wanted
OL,14,Fto, warning that flights might not be
OL,15,Favailable "over the coming days".
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
