PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772223642
OL,3,CUK withdraws staff from Iran amid
OL,4,Cthreat of US strikes
OL,6,FThe UK does not appear to have
OL,7,Fwithdrawn any staff from Israel, but
OL,8,Fcontinues to advise against travel to
OL,9,Fsome parts of the country for security
OL,10,Freasons.
OL,12,FOn Thursday, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,13,FStarmer said the UK was focused on
OL,14,F"supporting the political process"
OL,15,Fbetween Washington and Tehran.
