OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772223642
OL,3,CUK withdraws staff from Iran amid
OL,4,Cthreat of US strikes
OL,6,FThe UK is reported to have blocked a
OL,7,Frequest from Trump to use the Diego
OL,8,FGarcia base in the Chagos Islands in
OL,9,Fthe event that he decides to launch a
OL,10,Fmilitary campaign against Iran, due to
OL,11,Fconcerns it would breach international
OL,12,Flaw.
OL,14,FYou can hear Talking Politics wherever
OL,15,Fyou get your podcasts, including Apple
OL,16,FPodcasts and Spotify, and watch every
OL,17,Fepisode on YouTube and ITVX.
